List of years where races were completed.

Source: R/raceyears.R
raceyears.Rd

This function is for internal use by cyclingscraper and checkrace to ensure that HTML requests are only passed for years were a given race exists.

Usage

raceyears()

Value

A list containing race years for each race

Examples

raceyears()
